Program: Outlook
Title: Awake but Trapped Inside My Body
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswt6d
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Sep 2018
When Victoria Arlen was 11 years old, she became unwell with a mystery illness and lost consciousness. She only woke up years later to find herself in a hospital bed unable to communicate or move. For months she was alert, but nobody knew it and all she had were her thoughts. Image: silhouette of woman with hands pressed against a window Credit: Getty Images/coldsnowstorm Show less